{"tid":666263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"國民妹妹IU生日快樂！一起細數她的8大經典歌曲，你喜歡哪一首？","createTime":"2018-05-15T16:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T14:27:29.000Z","uid":34643,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8023cf9236c142f129ba3ed8871b722d5788940","tid":666263,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"IU生日快樂！偶像的外表及甜美嗓音使她收獲了大批粉絲，新歌一出便必定穩居音源榜單一位，歌影藝面面俱到的她更獲得&ldquo;國民妹妹&rdquo;稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Bg3EKho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBg3EKho.jpg&h=0cf193d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU全名李知恩，出生於1993年5月16日。她從小便喜愛唱歌，曾經到JYP參加練習生選拔，可惜落選。後來被現東家LOEN ENTERTAINMENT賞識，推出了不少膾炙人口的好歌。以下就為大家介紹一下IU的8大經典歌曲，讓大家感受一下她的魅力吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. Mia<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=3644047135,2951865708&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=333&amp;s=069E036D76114D705E08A16803006053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3644047135%2C2951865708%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D333%26s%3D069E036D76114D705E08A16803006053&h=9256a460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMia是IU的出道曲，於2008年發行。Mia是一首較為傷感的歌曲，歌詞不斷祈求離開的人回頭，雖然不少音樂人如柳熙烈都大贊她的實力，但當時年齡尚小的她未能以這首歌曲觸動人們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 嘮叨<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=940525440,2286319702&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=639&amp;h=313&amp;s=EEA0CC4B521830770C5C9C020300A053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D940525440%2C2286319702%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D639%26h%3D313%26s%3DEEA0CC4B521830770C5C9C020300A053&h=0cdd5c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘮叨是IU與2AM成員任瑟雍於2010年合唱的情歌。內容講述情侶之間甜蜜的吵嘴，調皮的歌詞剛好配合當時大熱的「亞當夫婦」趙權孫佳仁的互動，使這首歌為IU拿下首個音樂節目的一位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 好日子<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=759192765,2007656811&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=358&amp;s=CA902EC54861061D903775370300D048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D759192765%2C2007656811%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D358%26s%3DCA902EC54861061D903775370300D048&h=62efc213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這首歌是IU的成名曲，於2010年發行。這首充滿少女心的歌曲展現了IU的青春活力，當中的「三段高音」更成為眾人模仿但無法超越的傳奇。此歌為IU拿下MNET亞洲音樂盛典的最佳個人演唱獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. You &amp; I<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=1433677690,3631141828&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=363&amp;s=D23283291241C719E1ACF0D7030080B4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1433677690%2C3631141828%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D363%26s%3DD23283291241C719E1ACF0D7030080B4&h=5168e8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYou &amp; I於2011年發行，選用好日子的創作班底，延續該曲的熱潮。此曲由播出開始連續四周蟬聯冠軍，成為2011年最長期受歡迎的人氣歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 粉紅色高跟鞋<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=2574207000,1337208753&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=362&amp;s=9FBA67855A434AD21E31E1770300D073\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2574207000%2C1337208753%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D362%26s%3D9FBA67855A434AD21E31E1770300D073&h=f1260af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU於這首歌開始嘗試不同風格，這首歌發布於2013年，融入了30年代的曲風元素，黑暗童話式的風格令這首歌長居一位。同時該專輯《Modern Times》全部13首曲目一推出便占據了音源榜單1至13位，成績驕人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 星期五見面<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=1840026869,1287287726&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=367&amp;s=60C29145C1873378147DD80D03003081\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1840026869%2C1287287726%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D367%26s%3D60C29145C1873378147DD80D03003081&h=bb70c14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這首是和《Modern Times》同年發布的後續歌曲，由IU親自作曲作詞及演唱，表達了與戀人見面前的悸動。除了令人再次沉醉於IU清脆甜美的歌聲之外，更令人驚嘆其創作實力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. LEON<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=427992796,204536331&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=639&amp;h=362&amp;s=5AC4CE0954120DDA0C9031B403009080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D427992796%2C204536331%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D639%26h%3D362%26s%3D5AC4CE0954120DDA0C9031B403009080&h=9487d299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLEON是《無限挑戰》的歌謠祭特輯節目中制成的歌曲，由IU作曲作詞及樸明秀改編。兩者共同演唱的新鮮組合產生了意想不到的化學效果，不但取得Perfect all kill的佳績，更打破了《無限挑戰》的音源記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8. PALETTE<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=725207886,2716360988&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=289&amp;s=DDA87F7E1031F425C4DD80C30300B0A2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D725207886%2C2716360988%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D289%26s%3DDDA87F7E1031F425C4DD80C30300B0A2&h=e0a93a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPALETTE於去年發行，特意邀請到BIGBANG成員G-DRAGON演唱RAP的部份，與IU年輕時的青春舞曲不同，長大後的IU選擇了以簡單輕快的旋律唱出25歲的心態改變。"},{"pid":"ecdc73b584e12a4a2e6ab42f4c4c47c5af0f3ac8","tid":666263,"uid":154543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"PALETTE正 個MV影得佢好清純"},{"pid":"c9130cf1ef6d839ddc73a24322bcf0bd275bae98","tid":666263,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另加韓國本土熱門8首</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 秋日早晨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vQrDL9RZyYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvQrDL9RZyYw&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c15e89eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vQrDL9RZyYw</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 夜信<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VnoihuuZKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9VnoihuuZKc&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ac5d9b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VnoihuuZKc</a><br />\n<br />\n3. The Shower<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRTquokWSCw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTRTquokWSCw&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=509b09cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRTquokWSCw</a><br />\n<br />\n4. Knees<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1JUfCyeT5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL1JUfCyeT5E&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=00500b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1JUfCyeT5E</a><br />\n<br />\n5. The Meaning of You<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ss_U8UfQRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8ss_U8UfQRI&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=687c7149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ss_U8UfQRI</a><br />\n<br />\n6. Rain Drop<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oq2ERLpNwZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Doq2ERLpNwZQ&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7d88cae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oq2ERLpNwZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n7. Heart<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E42_mhziNHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE42_mhziNHo&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=38a88faa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E42_mhziNHo</a><br />\n<br />\n8. You Know<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_iEwq2zNwVY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_iEwq2zNwVY&d=91hdQvJiSf80uEaNMWSqMhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6638cdf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_iEwq2zNwVY</a>"},{"pid":"4db4a6aa816ab88f604938ee1